name: Ibukichi- Artist Style
description:
Ibukichi - Artist Style 🎨

This LoRA is trained on the great artworks of Ibukichi knowns for his round pillow like characters and warm color-pallet, check out his works on Twitter .

Usage Tips :

  • regular use is at the weight of 1 to 0.9 , still holds up at higher values.

  • adding ibukichi to the prompt will give the LoRA a tiny bit more influence.

  • This Style LoRA is fully capable of handling both SFW and NSFW prompts.

Samples Settings :

  • Checkpoints :anyhentai 19

  • Steps : 26

  • Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras

  • CFG : 7

Consider posting ur creation, I love to see what u make with it 😉
